data.text: @pete_folly @TheOnion Talk to your queen. She likes to use your taxes to host pedos, cheats and squirrel funds offshore too. I think a wedding which paid back more than was spent on it in tourist revenue is the least thing you need to worry about.
@TheOnion Means nothing to me. I don't know these people. I do, however, resent a slice of my taxes going to pay for their wedding whilst people in my country are forced to use food banks.
@TheOnion Good for them!. Wishing happiness and a lot children.😃
